NAME

DateTime::Locale::bm_ML - Locale data examples for the Bambara Mali (bm-ML) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Bambara Mali locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = tarata 5 feburuye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = juma 22 desanburu 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sibiri 15 sɛtanburu -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 feburuye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 desanburu 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 sɛtanburu -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 feb, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 des, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 sɛt, -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10
